					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Contribution:</strong> How to propose new components or tokens (e.g. request template, review process).</li>
					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Versioning:</strong> How we communicate breaking vs additive changes (link to changelog or "What's new").</li>
					<li class="mb-[0.35rem] text-doc-muted"><strong class="text-doc-text">Design tools:</strong> Where the canonical Figma library lives; how often it's synced with this doc.</li>
